{"word":"τρίτος","slug":"τρίτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>τρίτος, η, ον</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:τρεῖς\">τρεῖς</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> in serial sense <b>third<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a>, of living beings: human <b><a href='B:470 22:26'>Mt 22:26</a>; <a href='B:490 20:12'>Lk 20:12</a>, <a href='B:490 20:31'>31</a>;</b> angel <b><a href='B:730 14:19'>Rv 14:19</a>; <a href='B:730 16:4'>16:4</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a>, of things<b><p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>α.</pp></b> time, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἡμέρα\">ἡμέρα</a></el> <b><a href='B:470 16:21'>Mt 16:21</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a>; <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:φυλακή\">φυλακή</a></el> <b><a href='B:490 12:38'>Lk 12:38</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὥρα\">ὥρα</a></el> <b><a href='B:480 15:25'>Mk 15:25</a>; <a href='B:510 2:15'>Ac 2:15</a>; <a href='B:510 23:23'>23:23</a>.<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>β.</pp></b> other: heaven <b><a href='B:540 12:2'>2 Cor 12:2</a>;</b> seal <b><a href='B:730 6:5'>Rv 6:5</a>;</b> distress <b><a href='B:730 11:14'>11:14</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a>, (<el>τὸ</el>) <el>τρίτον</el> for the third time <b><a href='B:480 14:41'>Mk 14:41</a>; <a href='B:490 23:22'>Lk 23:22</a>; <a href='B:500 21:14'>J 21:14</a>, <a href='B:500 21:17'>17</a>; <a href='B:540 12:14'>2 Cor 12:14</a>, <a href='B:540 13:1'>13:1</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκ\">ἐκ</a> τρίτου</el> a third time <b><a href='B:470 26:44'>Mt 26:44</a>;</b> in enumeration: <el>τρίτον</el> third, thirdly <b><a href='B:530 12:28'>1 Cor 12:28</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> as noun in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to portion <el>τὸ τρίτον</el> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μέρος\">μέρος</a></el> understood) <b>third part <a href='B:730 8:7-12'>Rv 8:7-12</a>; <a href='B:730 9:15'>9:15</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:τρισχίλιοι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:τρίχες\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}